text.div:
HLA HGNC GeneID CodeSystem

CodeSystem of HLA gene group subset of HGNC GeneId Codesystem

Copyright Statement: National Human Genome Research Institute (NHGRI)

This code system http://www.genenames.org/geneId defines many codes, of which the following are a subset:
